cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it deals with the problem of music recommendation in the context of automatic playlist continuation. It also incorporates features from text and audio, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of Search and Discovery (cs.SD) and Speech and Signal Processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the use of Matrix Factorization and ranking fusion techniques indicates that it may belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computation and Language (cs.CL).
